 kill will be slower, however you will gain hps if not be full when you are done. and dont forget the lifetaps also do damage, if you can find a better tap weapon than bloodpoint, more power to ya.<br><br>now the epic 2h does not hold the best agro, it can hold agro very well with anger 3.usualy better than any normal 2 1handers with just anger 3 in both. or plain old hate / corel / bf / boc without augs. while taking less reposte.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
